is}}\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Awards for Ricky Gervais\n| list =\n{{British Academy Television Award for Best Comedy Performance}}\n{{BAFTA Los Angeles Britannia Awards}}\n{{EmmyAward ComedyLeadActor 2001-2025}}\n{{GoldenGlobeBestActorTVComedy 1990-2009}}\n{{Satellite Award Best Actor Motion Picture}}\n{{TCA Award for Individual Achievement in Comedy}}\n}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Gervais, Ricky}}\n[[Category:1961 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:20th-century British writers]]\n[[Category:20th-century English comedians]]\n[[Category:20th-century English male actors]]\n[[Category:20th-century atheists]]\n[[Category:21st-century British writers]]\n[[Category:21st-century English comedians]]\n[[Category:21st-century English male actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century atheists]]\n[[Category:Alumni of University College London]]\n[[Category:Atheism in the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:BAFTA winners (people)]]\n[[Category:Best Musical or Comedy Actor Golden Globe (television) winners]]\n[[Category:British atheism activists]]\n[[Category:British male comedy actors]]\n[[Category:British people of Canadian descent]]\n[[Category:British people of French-Canadian descent]]\n[[Category:British secularists]]\n[[Category:Comedy film directors]]\n[[Category:Critics of creationism]]\n[[Category:Critics of religions]]\n[[Category:Cultural critics]]\n[[Category:English atheists]]\n[[Category:English comedy writers]]\n[[Category:English film directors]]\n[[Category:English former Christians]]\n[[Category:English humanists]]\n[[Category:English humorists]]\n[[Category:English male comedians]]\n[[Category:English male film actors]]\n[[Category:English male screenwriters]]\n[[Category:English male television actors]]\n[[Category:English male voice actors]]\n[[Category:English new wave musicians]]\n[[Category:English people of Canadian descent]]\n[[Category:English people of French descent]]\n[[Category:English people of French-Canadian descent]]\n[[Category:Engli