ameras\">{{cite web |url=http://marsprogram.jpl.nasa.gov/msl/mission/rover/eyesandother/ |title=Mars Science Laboratory: Mission: Rover: Eyes and Other Senses: Four Engineering Hazcams (Hazard Avoidance Cameras) |publisher=NASA/JPL |accessdate=April 4, 2009}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Mars Hand Lens Imager (MAHLI)\">{{cite web |url=http://msl-scicorner.jpl.nasa.gov/Instruments/MAHLI/ |title=Mars Hand Lens Imager (MAHLI) |first=Kenneth S. |last=Edgett |publisher=NASA |accessdate=January 11, 2012}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"NASA-20120913\">{{cite web |title=3D View of MAHLI Calibration Target |url=http://mars.jpl.nasa.gov/multimedia/images/?ImageID=4664 |date=September 13, 2012 |publisher=[[NASA]] |accessdate=October 11, 2012}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"MSLAPXS\">{{cite web |url=http://msl-scicorner.jpl.nasa.gov/Instruments/APXS/ |title=MSL Science Corner: Alpha Particle X-ray Spectrometer (APXS) |publisher=NASA/JPL |accessdate=September 9, 2009}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"usra\">{{cite web |url=http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2009/pdf/2364.pdf |title=40th Lunar and Planetary Science Conference |last= |first= |website= |year=2009}}<br />{{cite web |url=http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2010/pdf/2539.pdf |title=41st Lunar and Planetary Science Conference |last= |first= |website= |year=2010}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"The new Athena alpha particle X-ray spectrometer for the Mars Exploration Rovers\">{{cite journal |title=The new Athena alpha particle X-ray spectrometer for the Mars Exploration Rovers |first=R. |last=Rieder |first2=R. |last2=Gellert |first3=J. |last3=Br\u00fcckner |first4=G. |last4=Klingelh\u00f6fer |first5=G. |last5=Dreibus |first6=A. |last6=Yen |first7=S. W. |last7=Squyres |display-authors=5 |journal=[[Journal of Geophysical Research]] |year=2003 |volume=108 |issue=E12 |page=8066 |doi=10.1029/2003JE002150 |bibcode=2003JGRE..108.8066R}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"NASA-20121030\">{{cite web |last=Brown |first=Dwayne |title=NASA Rover's First Soil Studies Help Fingerprint Martian Minerals 